"If music is the soul of love,then play on"
Hy Shoshay, Wooow What a true picture of War and peace,This mentor has portrayed in his austhetic way of his poetry.
He say what Shakespeare's had said 6th century ago that is "This world is nothing but illusion and delusion...and Oh thy  Lord,what a fool of  this mortal be",But this mentor says" Sab Maya hay" mean " Everything is illusion" This world is nothing but a dream,Where everyone  play the role of An Actor and play many part of  Action at the same time". This songs touch my sense and sensibility without deviating my real dream for Maya World. Many thanks for All those and that who love and share love... Because this is the one and only weapons through which we can conquer the rough 💓 of Hitler's mind people.
